<template><section>

<h2 id="navmenu-dao-hang-cai-dan"><a class="header-anchor" href="#navmenu-dao-hang-cai-dan" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> NavMenu 导航菜单</h2>
<p>为网站提供导航功能的菜单。</p>
<h3 id="ding-lan"><a class="header-anchor" href="#ding-lan" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> 顶栏</h3>
<p>适用广泛的基础用法。</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-menu theme=\&quot;dark\&quot; :default-active=\&quot;activeIndex\&quot; class=\&quot;el-menu-demo\&quot; mode=\&quot;horizontal\&quot; @select=\&quot;handleSelect\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;1\&quot;&gt;处理中心&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n  &lt;el-submenu index=\&quot;2\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;template slot=\&quot;title\&quot;&gt;我的工作台&lt;/template&gt;\n    &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;2-1\&quot;&gt;选项1&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n    &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;2-2\&quot;&gt;选项2&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n    &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;2-3\&quot;&gt;选项3&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n  &lt;/el-submenu&gt;\n  &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;3\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://www.ele.me\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&gt;订单管理&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n&lt;/el-menu&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;line\&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;el-menu :default-active=\&quot;activeIndex2\&quot; class=\&quot;el-menu-demo\&quot; mode=\&quot;horizontal\&quot; @select=\&quot;handleSelect\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;1\&quot;&gt;处理中心&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n  &lt;el-submenu index=\&quot;2\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;template slot=\&quot;title\&quot;&gt;我的工作台&lt;/template&gt;\n    &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;2-1\&quot;&gt;选项1&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n    &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;2-2\&quot;&gt;选项2&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n    &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;2-3\&quot;&gt;选项3&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n  &lt;/el-submenu&gt;\n  &lt;el-menu-item index=\&quot;3\&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://www.ele.me\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot;&gt;订单管理&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/el-menu-item&gt;\n&lt;/el-menu&gt;\n\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\n  export default {\n    data() {\n      return {\n        activeIndex: '1',\n        activeIndex2: '1'\n      };\n    },\n    methods: {\n      handleSelect(key, keyPath) {\n        console.log(key, keyPath);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-menu theme="dark" :default-active="activeIndex" class="el-menu-demo" mode="horizontal" @select="handleSelect">
  <el-menu-item index="1">处理中心</el-menu-item>
  <el-submenu index="2">
    <template slot="title">我的工作台</template>
    <el-menu-item index="2-1">选项1</el-menu-item>
    <el-menu-item index="2-2">选项2</el-menu-item>
    <el-menu-item index="2-3">选项3</el-menu-item>
  </el-submenu>
  <el-menu-item index="3"><a href="https://www.ele.me" target="_blank">订单管理</a></el-menu-item>
</el-menu>
<div class="line"></div>
<el-menu :default-active="activeIndex2" class="el-menu-demo" mode="horizontal" @select="handleSelect">
  <el-menu-item index="1">处理中心</el-menu-item>
  <el-submenu index="2">
    <template slot="title">我的工作台</template>
    <el-menu-item index="2-1">选项1</el-menu-item>
    <el-menu-item index="2-2">选项2</el-menu-item>
    <el-menu-item index="2-3">选项3</el-menu-item>
  </el-submenu>
  <el-menu-item index="3"><a href="https://www.ele.me" target="_blank">订单管理</a></el-menu-item>
</el-menu>


</div>
                    <p>导航菜单默认为垂直模式，通过 <code>mode</code> 属性可以使导航菜单变更为水平模式。另外，在菜单中通过 <code>submenu</code> 组件可以生成二级菜单。</p>

